      <title>英国经济衰退以解除封锁以来最强劲的增长结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/uk-says-recession-ended-with-stronger-than-expected-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国从轻微衰退中强势反弹，为首相里希·苏纳克（Rishi Sunak）带来了一些安慰，他迄今为止仍在努力兑现发展经济的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/uk-says-recession-ended-with-stronger-than-expected-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 06:05:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗下调中国股市评级，上调印度股市盈利前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/citi-cuts-china-stocks-on-fundamentals-to-neutral-raises-india</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团的策略师将高速发展的中国股市评级下调至中性，认为尽管基本面疲软，但近期的反弹还是出现了。该团队将新兴市场竞争对手印度的评级上调至“增持”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/citi-cuts-china-stocks-on-fundamentals-to-neutral-raises-india</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 05:10:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
